32#ifndef _DRM_DRM_TRACE_NETBSD_H_
33#define _DRM_DRM_TRACE_NETBSD_H_
34
35#include <sys/sdt.h>
36
37#ifdef CREATE_TRACE_POINTS
38#define DEFINE_TRACE0(m,p,n) SDT_PROBE_DEFINE0(sdt,m,p,n)
39#define DEFINE_TRACE1(m,p,n,a) SDT_PROBE_DEFINE1(sdt,m,p,n,a)
40#define DEFINE_TRACE2(m,p,n,a,b) SDT_PROBE_DEFINE2(sdt,m,p,n,a,b)
41#define DEFINE_TRACE3(m,p,n,a,b,c) SDT_PROBE_DEFINE3(sdt,m,p,n,a,b,c)
42#define DEFINE_TRACE4(m,p,n,a,b,c,d) SDT_PROBE_DEFINE4(sdt,m,p,n,a,b,c,d)
43#define DEFINE_TRACE5(m,p,n,a,b,c,d,e) SDT_PROBE_DEFINE5(sdt,m,p,n,a,b,c,d,e)
44#define DEFINE_TRACE6(m,p,n,a,b,c,d,e,f) \
45 SDT_PROBE_DEFINE6(sdt,m,p,n,a,b,c,d,e,f)
46#define DEFINE_TRACE7(m,p,n,a,b,c,d,e,f,g) \
47 SDT_PROBE_DEFINE7(sdt,m,p,n,a,b,c,d,e,f,g)
48#else
49#define DEFINE_TRACE0(m,p,n) SDT_PROBE_DECLARE(sdt,m,p,n)
50#define DEFINE_TRACE1(m,p,n,a) SDT_PROBE_DECLARE(sdt,m,p,n)
51#define DEFINE_TRACE2(m,p,n,a,b) SDT_PROBE_DECLARE(sdt,m,p,n)
52#define DEFINE_TRACE3(m,p,n,a,b,c) SDT_PROBE_DECLARE(sdt,m,p,n)
53#define DEFINE_TRACE4(m,p,n,a,b,c,d) SDT_PROBE_DECLARE(sdt,m,p,n)
54#define DEFINE_TRACE5(m,p,n,a,b,c,d,e) SDT_PROBE_DECLARE(sdt,m,p,n)
55#define DEFINE_TRACE6(m,p,n,a,b,c,d,e,f) \
56 SDT_PROBE_DECLARE(sdt,m,p,n)
57#define DEFINE_TRACE7(m,p,n,a,b,c,d,e,f,g) \
58 SDT_PROBE_DECLARE(sdt,m,p,n)
59#endif
60
61#define TRACE0(m,p,n) SDT_PROBE0(sdt,m,p,n)
62#define TRACE1(m,p,n,a) SDT_PROBE1(sdt,m,p,n,a)
63#define TRACE2(m,p,n,a,b) SDT_PROBE2(sdt,m,p,n,a,b)
64#define TRACE3(m,p,n,a,b,c) SDT_PROBE3(sdt,m,p,n,a,b,c)
65#define TRACE4(m,p,n,a,b,c,d) SDT_PROBE4(sdt,m,p,n,a,b,c,d)
66#define TRACE5(m,p,n,a,b,c,d,e) SDT_PROBE5(sdt,m,p,n,a,b,c,d,e)
67#define TRACE6(m,p,n,a,b,c,d,e,f) SDT_PROBE6(sdt,m,p,n,a,b,c,d,e,f)
68#define TRACE7(m,p,n,a,b,c,d,e,f,g) SDT_PROBE7(sdt,m,p,n,a,b,c,d,e,f,g)
69
70#endif /* _LINUX_TRACEPOINT_H_ */
